<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>214</hymn_number>
<title>JESUH TUM THAN TIANG KAN TUAN LAI CH214</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Sifahnak in ruahchan ram tha, Zeitikdah ka phak lai? Zeitikah ralthuam
 ka chiah lai, Hnangamnak ka hmuh lai?

[C1]
   Jesuh (Jesuh) tum than tiangin, Hngak ko, (hngak ko) a tum hlan
   tiang, Riantuan (riantuan) a dih tikah, Inn tha chung kan um lai.

[V2]
 Vawlei cung hnangamnak um lo, Zeihmanh a tling kho lo, Vawlei cung sau
 nuamhnak um lo, Sifah nak ram a si.

[C2]
   Jesuh (Jesuh) tum than tiangin, Hngak ko, (hngak ko) a tum hlan
   tiang, Riantuan (riantuan) a dih tikah, Inn tha chung kan um lai.

[V3]
 Hnangam le sunpar hmuh awkah, Lam dang va pial ti hlah, Vancung khua
 tha kan phak hlan tiang, A kan hruai zungzal lai.

[C3]
   Jesuh (Jesuh) tum than tiangin, Hngak ko, (hngak ko) a tum hlan
   tiang, Riantuan (riantuan) a dih tikah, Inn tha chung kan um lai.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
</song>